      "text": "\n\nTask 3\n(MPU)\n\nUpload DMP\n\nCalibrate MPU\n\nRead Raw values\n\nSend data to Task2 \n\nSet the Motion on wakeup interrupt\n\nsend the MPU to sleep?",
