      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "\n\nTask 4\n(SETUP MODE)\n\nStart AP MODE TO Host website\n\nPaused every task\n\nshows reading from each sensor\n\nShows Serial Terminal\n\nCalibrate MPU\n\nTest Hooters\n\nAssign TID\n\nOTA Update\n\nSet coordinates of system\n\nResume tasks ",
      "fontSize": 36,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": "nrlf0Vc1qK2CXtTTbpt7z",
      "originalText": "\n\nTask 4\n(SETUP MODE)\n\nStart AP MODE TO Host website\n\nPaused every task\n\nshows reading from each sensor\n\nShows Serial Terminal\n\nCalibrate MPU\n\nTest Hooters\n\nAssign TID\n\nOTA Update\n\nSet coordinates of system\n\nResume tasks ",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
