      "seed": 1024864304,
      "version": 340,
      "versionNonce": 1291742128,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1777712964868,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "\n\nTask 2\n(GSM)\n\nConnet to Internet \n\nWaits untill all the data is recived\n\nSends the data tries for 5 times until,\nretire\n\nSends the GSM to Sleep \n\nSends ESP to sleep for 10 mins\n\n",
      "fontSize": 36,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": "xQD6-bL9KgKW1uymZTBO0",
      "originalText": "\n\nTask 2\n(GSM)\n\nConnet to Internet \n\nWaits untill all the data is recived\n\nSends the data tries for 5 times until, retire\n\nSends the GSM to Sleep \n\nSends ESP to sleep for 10 mins\n\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
