      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1777713242256,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Rain\n\nincrement RAIN variable by one\n\nA circular buffer of 10 \n\n1st interrupt if sum of buffer is 0 \nsend data(initialise setup)\n\nif it is not the 1st buffer then send\nthe data when esp wakes(go to\nsleep imeddeatly)",
      "fontSize": 36,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "uEN4ZnOaU_dGbR0svA-Qb",
      "originalText": "Rain\n\nincrement RAIN variable by one\n\nA circular buffer of 10 \n\n1st interrupt if sum of buffer is 0 \nsend data(initialise setup)\n\nif it is not the 1st buffer then send the data when esp wakes(go to sleep imeddeatly)",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
